T1  - Strategic Issue Management Systems: Forms, Functions, and Contexts
AU  - Dutton, Jane E.
AU  - Ottensmeyer, Edward
Y1  - 1987/04/01
PY  - 1987
DA  - 1987/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1987.4307971
